cs.LG, cs.AR, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper is about reducing the numerical precision of computations in deep learning training, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and neural networks (cs.NE). The paper also discusses the hardware implementation of these computations, which falls under the category of computer architecture (cs.AR) and systems and control (cs.SY).
